## Appendix: minimum cost estimate

Phase 1 (pre-customer) baseline, monthly:

| Resource | Cost |
|---|---|
| Cloud Run (min=0, idle) | $0 |
| Cloud SQL `db-f1-micro` | ~$8 |
| GCS standard (1 GB) | ~$0.02 |
| Cloud Tasks | $0 (well under free tier) |
| Cloud Scheduler (~2 jobs) | $0 (free tier) |
| Secret Manager (~9 secrets, low access) | ~$0.50 |
| Artifact Registry (1 GB) | ~$0.10 |
| **Total fixed** | **~$9/month** |

Add per-request external API costs on top — see your Tech Stack design doc
for the full cost model.
